No. 301. Eliza L. Pope, Plaintiff in Error, v. Anna Clara Falk et al. In error to the Supreme Court of- the State of Kansas. April 2, 1906. Mr. L. F. Bird for plaintiff in error. Mr. James K. Polk, Mr. Andrew Wüson and Mr. Noel W. Barksdale for defendants in error.

Dismissed with costs, on-motion of counsel for plaintiff in error.
